{"tid":571172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"做個調查，有幾多連登仔支持/反對填海？","createTime":"2018-02-24T12:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T14:43:16.000Z","uid":35870,"like":46,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4daa42848f6029b7194fda11895802d9387eeb59","tid":571172,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T12:00:53.000Z","msg":"唔好講咩停百五呀，用晒棕地丁地golf地d野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(假設百五繼續黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反對<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c9c5002b1592baa87df3d91cd3f80b7d565411","tid":571172,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce460ae5c0c03b353fbfb6e134c5c2cc24ba088b","tid":571172,"uid":53186,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T17:46:37.000Z","msg":"填海不嬲唔係問題,香港就係靠填海發展起家,就算150繼續嚟,點都需要搵地發展<br />\n唔搵地發展,150一樣唔會停,到時仲衰,人人住劏房/瞓街<br />\n<br />\nbtw,香港最反填海嘅一係地產商,一係臨海樓業主"},{"pid":"0cfb6a5fa93531198c7838ebef32e774538bf1de","tid":571172,"uid":87511,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T18:00:52.000Z","msg":"細細個畀啲環保撚洗哂腦<br />\n講啲咩中華白海豚乜乜柒柒<br />\n所以就會覺得填海唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  邊個填海邊個就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家大個咗<br />\n心諗大把香港人仲慘撚過啲海豚啦<br />\n仲走去關心啲本身已經就快絕種嘅海豚做乜鳩"},{"pid":"75216dd8fd05cab5ba9e6ff23c6f8f81ec8b3f8e","tid":571172,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:39:09.000Z","msg":"好多無保育爭議既位可以填"},{"pid":"4f01d6ab17b09089b2a48b142aea0d482779ffd4","tid":571172,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislik